### Get all bribes
GET http://localhost:3000/api/bribes

# ============================================================================
# SEARCHS
# ============================================================================

### Search by status - paid bribes (paid=true)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/bribes/search?paid=true

### Search by status - pending bribes (paid=false)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/bribes/search?paid=false

### Search by creation date - exact (specific day)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/bribes/search?date=2025-10-06&type=exact

### Search by creation date - after (from that date onwards)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/bribes/search?date=2025-09-01&type=after

### Search by creation date - before (until that date)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/bribes/search?date=2025-12-31&type=before

### Search by creation date - between (range between two dates)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/bribes/search?date=2025-09-01&endDate=2025-11-30&type=between

# ============================================================================
# CRUD
# ============================================================================

### Get a bribe by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/bribes/5

### Pay bribe to a specific authority
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/bribes/10101013/pay
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids":[5]
}

### Pay multiple bribes (without filtering by authority)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/bribes/pay
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids": [2, 3, 5]
}

### Delete a bribe by ID
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/bribes/4